childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in&Hyrule...^$0%gForest Temple%w...^$1%rSpirit Temple%w...^$2%bJabu-Jabu's Belly%w...^$oYe who may become a Hero...&The path to the future is open...

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the&Sacred Realm will call those&destined to be Sages, who dwell&in the %rfive temples%w.^$8%yDeku Tree%w...^$3%gWater Temple%w...^$4%rLink's Pocket%w...^$5%bShadow Temple%w...^$6%yDodongo's Cavern%w...^$7%pFire Temple%w...^$lThe awakened ones will await for&the Hero to find %gGreg%w.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will be&provided by Zelda once %r5&Spiritual Stones and Medallions%w&are retrieved.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me by&reflecting my lightning bolts and&unleashing the arrows from %rHyrule&Field%w!^And even if you do, you'll never&find the legendary blade hidden in&%rKakariko Village%w!
dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%rthe Lost Woods%w. I will let you have&my stretching, shrinking keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Damp√©
gregText: By the way, if you're interested, I&saw the shiniest %gGreen Rupee%w&somewhere in%g Gerudo Valley%w.^It's said to have %rmysterious&powers%w...^But then, it could just be another&regular rupee.&Oh well.
sariaText: Did you feel the %gsurge of magic%w&recently? A mysterious bird told&me it came from %gZora's River%w.^You should check that place out,&@!$C
